						<b>Airtank temperature: </b>[tank_temperature]&deg;K|[tank_temperature - T0C]&deg;C<br>
						<b>Cabin pressure: </b>[cabin_pressure>WARNING_HIGH_PRESSURE ? "<span class='danger'>[cabin_pressure]</span>": cabin_pressure]kPa<br>
